Package com.googlecode.wickedcharts.highcharts.options.processing

Interface Summary
IOptionsProcessor Interface for processing Options before they are renderer.
 

Class Summary
IdGeneratorProcessor This IOptionsProcessor assigns a unique ID to all Series, Axis and Points that are contained in an Options object.
OptionsProcessorContext A context object that holds some context variables that may be needed by IOptionsProcessors.
